<Base title="SocialProof for Travel Agents — Client Testimonials That Book More Trips | SocialProof" description="Travel agents and agencies: collect client testimonials with a simple link and display them on your website. SocialProof helps you build the trust that converts browsers into booked travelers.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Travel Agents
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        People trust travel agents with their vacations — their money, their time, and their most anticipated moments of the year. That trust has to be earned before they ever reach out. SocialProof helps travel agents and agencies collect client testimonials and display them where they convert: on your website, before the first inquiry.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why travel agents need social proof more than ever</h2>
      <p>With OTAs like Expedia and Google Flights just a click away, travel agents compete on one thing: personal expertise and peace of mind. Testimonials prove you deliver trips that go smoothly, find deals clients couldn't find themselves, and handle the unexpected when it happens. That proof is your moat against the algorithms.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Testimonials that book more trips</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Expertise that saves money:</strong> "She got us into a category-5 suite on our cruise for less than we'd paid for a category-3 on our own last year."</li>
        <li><strong>The personal touch:</strong> "He remembered my wife's shellfish allergy and pre-arranged special meals at every restaurant on our itinerary."</li>
        <li><strong>When things go wrong:</strong> "Our flight was cancelled mid-trip. She had us rebooked and at our hotel before the airline even acknowledged the problem."</li>
        <li><strong>Destination expertise:</strong> "She'd personally been to Tuscany seven times. Every recommendation was perfect. No tourist traps."</li>
        <li><strong>Honeymoon magic:</strong> "Our honeymoon was beyond anything we imagined. She thought of details we never would have known to ask for."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for travel agencies</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Add the widget</strong> to your homepage and destination-specific pages.</li>
        <li><strong>After clients return from their trip</strong>, send them your SocialProof link — when the memories are fresh and the gratitude is high.</li>
        <li><strong>Clients share their experience</strong> — no login, no lengthy form, just a natural text box.</li>
        <li><strong>You approve each testimonial</strong> before it goes live on your site.</li>
        <li><strong>Organize by destination or trip type</strong> — honeymoon testimonials near your honeymoon page, cruise testimonials near cruises, etc.</li>
      </ol>

      <div style="background:#fdf4ff;border:1px solid #e9d5ff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#6b21a8;">
          "After every trip, I send clients the SocialProof link in my follow-up email. I've built up 35+ testimonials in 4 months. New inquiries now often say they read the reviews and knew immediately they wanted to work with me."
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#581c87;">— Independent travel advisor, specializing in luxury Europe</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Start free</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget. Start turning happy travelers into your best marketing — no credit card required.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <a href="/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
          Start collecting testimonials free
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;">Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
      </div>
